---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Company - Services">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Our Services
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400">
        Comprehensive solutions tailored to your needs
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mb-4">Energy-as-a-Service</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400">
        We design, install, own, 
        and operate the sand battery system while customers pay only for delivered heat under a long-term service agreement. 
        This model eliminates capital expenditure and reduces operational risk while providing stable, affordable thermal energy..</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold mb-4">Direct Purchase</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400">Clients purchase and own the sand battery system as part of their energy infrastructure. We provide engineering design, installation, commissioning, and ongoing technical support to ensure optimal performance and longevity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
